headline: Jabil Announces Annual Meeting of Stockholders
summary: ST. PETERSBURG, Fla., January 13, 2026--Jabil Inc. (NYSE: JBL) today announced it will host its Annual Meeting of Stockholders in a virtual only format on January 22, 2026, at 10:00 a.m. EST.
